      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds so... empty. If it's all just an illusion and a glitch, then why even try to hold onto it? It feels like fighting against something that's already decided I'm gone. It just seems exhausting to keep existing if the end result is just being a 'forgotten memory' anyway.",
